  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Titlis Resort apartments are offered on a self-catering board basis and provide you with a fully equipped kitchenette and dining area.</p>
<p>The apartment building is only a short walk from the village centre where you'll find a range of bars and restaurants serving local, Swiss cuisine to international dishes.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>0</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>Conveniently situated in the heart of Engelberg, Titlis Resort places you just a short stroll away from the TITLIS valley station, the train station and the village centre. Titlis Resort offers contemporary and cosy apartments and is the perfect choice for those of you who love to be independent and feel at home on your winter holidays.</span></p>
<h2>Fantastic range of wellness facilities </h2>
<p>At Titlis Resort, there are wellness facilities for everyone. Included in your stay is access to the apartment buildings Wellness Oasis centre which has some excellent facilities for you to use to really sit back and relax after an energetic day on the slopes. Soothe your muscles in the Finnish sauna, steam bath or multi-sensory shower. If you'd prefer to give your body some extra loving, you can book a day package through Titlis Resort's private spa, where you'll have access to some exclusive facilities like a whirlpool and waterbed and you'll even get a professional massage.</p>
<h2>Comfortable, attractive apartments </h2>
<p><span>Experience the comfort of 'home' throughout your stay in one of these apartments. These apartments are modern and furnished to a high standard with a traditional, wooden alpine feel throughout. The spacious and well-lit living space, complete with an open-plan kitchen and dining area, offers a great base for a social getaway with your friends and family. </span></p>]]></description>
