  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>Ski and boot storage room - each apartment is given a specific locker with boot dryers</li>
<li>Bike storage room </li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Wellness oasis with access to a Finnish sauna (16 years and over), herbal bath, steam bath, ice shower, multi-sensory shower, quiet lounge and spa garden </li>
<li>Book a day of exclusive spa facilities with the hotel's private spa including access to a solo-whirlpool, salt stone sauna, steam bath, multi-sensory shower, waterbed, heated seating, bathrobes and slippers and a relaxing massage</li>
<li>Towels are provided for all spa experiences</li>
<li>YOU beauty treatments and massages available at an extra charge </li>
</ul>
<p>Entry to the wellness oasis is included with your stay. The day spa and massages or beauty treatments are available at a local charge. <span>The "Sonnenberg" public swimming pool is just 5 minutes' walk from TITLIS Resort.</span></p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Family Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Two outdoor play areas, including table tennis</li>
<li>Cards and dice games can be borrowed from reception </li>
<li>Baby kits are available upon request and include cots, high chairs, children's tableware, potty or toilet seat attachments, baby baths and a changing mat</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
