  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>One bedroom apartments </strong>are between <span>47 - 59m² sleeping two to four people. These apartments have an open plan living and kitchenette/dining area with a double sofa bed. There is one double bedroom as well as a bathroom with either a shower or a bathtub. </span></p>
<p><strong>Two bedroom apartments </strong>are between 73 - 92m² sleeping four to six people. <span>These apartments have an open plan living and kitchenette/dining area with a double sofa bed. There is one double bedroom and one twin bedroom. These apartments also have one bathroom with a bathtub and a shower room both with WCs. </span><span></span></p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Apartment facilities:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>All apartments have either a balcony or patio area</li>
<li>All apartments can take cots upon request </li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi </li>
<li>A fully equipped kitchenette</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
